functionDecorators.name: diamondCut
functionDecorators.description: Add/replace/remove any number of functions and optionally execute a function with delegatecall.

parameterDecorators.name: _diamondCut
parameterDecorators.description: Contains the facet addresses and function selectors.

parameterDecorators.name: _init
parameterDecorators.description: The address of the contract or facet to execute _calldata.

parameterDecorators.name: _calldata
parameterDecorators.description: A function call, including function selector and arguments _calldata is executed with delegatecall on _init.

functionDecorators.name: facetAddress
functionDecorators.description: Gets the facet that supports the given selector. If facet is not found return address(0).

functionDecorators.name: facetAddresses
functionDecorators.description: Get all the facet addresses used by a diamond.

functionDecorators.name: facetFunctionSelectors
functionDecorators.description: Gets all the function selectors provided by a facet.

functionDecorators.name: facets
functionDecorators.description: Gets all facets and their selectors.

functionDecorators.name: renounceOwnership
functionDecorators.description: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

functionDecorators.name: supportsInterface
functionDecorators.description: query whether contract has registered support for given interface.

functionDecorators.name: transferOwnership
functionDecorators.description: transfer contract ownership to new account.
